tspan.tspan: Asynch msg -- A sends an asynchronous message to B
Synch msg -- A sends a synchronous message to B
Aggregation -- A is contained without beloning to B
Composition -- A is contained and is owned by B
Directed assoc (has-ref-to) -- Can navigate from A to B
Dependence -- A depends (param, var, ret-val) upon B
Realization -- A is a realization of the abstract class B
